    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"4269\" data-end=\"4308\">Badger’s Burrow — Zone of Awareness</strong><br data-start=\"4308\" data-end=\"4311\" /><em data-start=\"4311\" data-end=\"4347\">Caern State (from Badger’s Burrow)</em></p><p data-start=\"4349\" data-end=\"4408\">The Caern listens for disturbance within a designated zone.</p><p data-start=\"4410\" data-end=\"4596\"><strong data-start=\"4410\" data-end=\"4423\">Duration:</strong> Until the end of the current <strong data-start=\"4453\" data-end=\"4467\">Caern Turn</strong><br data-start=\"4467\" data-end=\"4470\" /><strong data-start=\"4470\" data-end=\"4486\">Zone Radius:</strong> Based on Caern Rating (1=60ft, 2=120ft, 3=300ft, 4=1000ft, 5=1 mile)<br data-start=\"4555\" data-end=\"4558\" /><strong data-start=\"4558\" data-end=\"4575\">Center Point:</strong> (set by script / GM)</p><p data-start=\"4598\" data-end=\"4610\"><strong data-start=\"4598\" data-end=\"4610\">Benefits</strong></p><ul data-start=\"4611\" data-end=\"4923\"><li data-start=\"4611\" data-end=\"4761\"><p data-start=\"4613\" data-end=\"4628\">ST alerts when:</p><ul data-start=\"4631\" data-end=\"4761\"><li data-start=\"4631\" data-end=\"4654\"><p data-start=\"4633\" data-end=\"4654\">creatures enter/leave</p></li><li data-start=\"4657\" data-end=\"4702\"><p data-start=\"4659\" data-end=\"4702\">hostile/stealth/clandestine activity occurs</p></li><li data-start=\"4705\" data-end=\"4761\"><p data-start=\"4707\" data-end=\"4761\">rituals/corruption/supernatural influence is attempted</p></li></ul></li><li data-start=\"4762\" data-end=\"4864\"><p data-start=\"4764\" data-end=\"4864\">Garou tending the Caern: advantage on Perception/Survival to investigate events from within the zone</p></li><li data-start=\"4865\" data-end=\"4923\"><p data-start=\"4867\" data-end=\"4923\">Creatures bypassing notice within the zone: disadvantage</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"4925\" data-end=\"5000\"><strong data-start=\"4925\" data-end=\"4934\">Limit</strong><br />Conveys presence/disturbance, not exact identity/location/intent.</p><p data-start=\"5002\" data-end=\"5143\"><strong data-start=\"5002\" data-end=\"5026\">Tag (do not remove):</strong><br data-start=\"5026\" data-end=\"5029\" /><code data-start=\"5029\" data-end=\"5143\">[GAROU_CAERN_STATE] parent=badgers-burrow; effect=zone-of-awareness; cadence=turn; exclusiveGroup=badgers-burrow</code></p>",
